posts.post_title: Looking to buy 1909 Cuban Cabanas Baseball cards
posts.post_content: Any condition. Let me know what you have and let's work out a deal. Cash or trade fine with me. I have some other early Cuban issues, postcards and interesting trade material.

Brian Van Horn has a Davy Jones Cabanas. Message him, if he hasn't messaged you yet.

These are awesome cards. I definitely still need to add one to my collection.

-Nick
